==Synopsis==
Mariama and her blind son Bilaly are shunned by their neighbours. When Mariama rescues an [[albinism|albino]] man, Samba from drowning, she discovers that he is a healer and can cure her son's blindness. In order for him to do this, Mariama must commit incest with Bilaly.<ref>{{Cite web
  | title = Denko
  | work = 
  | publisher = [[British Film Institute]] National Archive
  | date = 2 December 2009
  | url = http://www.bfi.org.uk/nftva/access/catalogues/film/3/533/1538
  | format = 
  | doi = 
  | accessdate =5 February 2010 }}
</ref>
